readme:
Service Usage

This service is used by consumers to request payment and generate an invoice for a product or service which has been provided by the department. Although product codes are required in the payload, the consumer maintains responsibility for defining the total amount payable.

Service Behaviour

Upon creation of the invoice and for subsequent updates to the transaction, the provider will invoke a EV029-NotifyProductPaymentStatus.
